data.meta_description: Anastasia Agmunda Rurikids of Kiev, Queen of Hungary was born in the year 1023 in Kiev, Kievian Rus (present Ukraine), daughter of Yaroslav "The Wise" Grand Prince of Kiev and Ingegerd (Estrid,Astrid,Alvhild) Olofsdotter of Sweden, Swedish princess and a Grand Princess of Kiev., they gave birth to 1 child. She died in the year 1074 in Admont Abbey, Austria. This information is part of Family tree Cromer/Russell/Buck/Pratt by Elizabeth Cromer on Genealogy Online.
